    "h. The association of molecular categories and HOXB subclusters.",
    "The statistical significance of the enrichment and exclusivity were calculated and shown as in d. Extended Data Fig. 9 | Clinical association of molecular categories and known prognostic factors in the AAML1031 cohort.",
